11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_CONTROLLER_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_CONTROLLER_H_
13
14#include "absl/types/optional.h"
15#include "modules/audio_coding/audio_network_adaptor/include/audio_network_adaptor.h"
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19class Controller {
20 public:
21 struct NetworkMetrics {
22 NetworkMetrics();
23 ~NetworkMetrics();
24 absl::optional<int> uplink_bandwidth_bps;
25 absl::optional<float> uplink_packet_loss_fraction;
26 absl::optional<int> target_audio_bitrate_bps;
27 absl::optional<int> rtt_ms;
28 absl::optional<size_t> overhead_bytes_per_packet;
29 };
30
31 virtual ~Controller() = default;
32
33 // Informs network metrics update to this controller. Any non-empty field
34 // indicates an update on the corresponding network metric.
35 virtual void UpdateNetworkMetrics(const NetworkMetrics& network_metrics) = 0;
36
37 virtual void MakeDecision(AudioEncoderRuntimeConfig* config) = 0;
38};
39
40} // namespace webrtc
41
42#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_CONTROLLER_H_
